{
  "stem": "25773.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it is prevalent in the-- in the-- in the Polish gastronomic sort of kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the kitchen, a gastronomic recipes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A soup is made of goose blood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Goose blood?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Blood.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Blood.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They do it to all kinds of things, and it's actually very good.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know about it, and we were always hungry, young people, so we ate the soup with goose blood and God knows what afterwards.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And afterwards, we found out that Krystyna told me, this is goose blood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Masia, ?] I remember, she never went out of the toilet for maybe six hours.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She will sick and sick and sick and sick till she was completely dehydrated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It didn't harm me somehow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she was completely dehydrated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We felt very, very, very unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because blood, in our religion, is one thing we mustn't eat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We drain our meat from blood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And blood-- and there-- she's-- she said she's contaminated for-- for life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anyway, we worked there, and we helped the-- the-- the lady, the farmer's wife.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "No, eventually we reach Bobrovnik, yes, in a grand style because at the end, we found a-- a priest who was going to-- to marry somebody, and he was going with the horse and cart.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he saw us poor girls working, so he invited us to this-- to-- also to this wedding.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we-- we-- we-- we went with him to the wedding.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We did go to the actual wedding because we were not dressed properly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we were at this very wealthy farm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he was going to Bobrovnik, and we arrived in great style.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we found out that were are in the middle of German milieu again.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
